title: Agreement with St Louis Food Hub TIF

abstracts.abstract: BOARD BILL #295	INTRODUCED BY ALDERWOMAN PHYLLIS YOUNG    An Ordinance Affirming Adoption Of A Redevelopment Plan, Redevelopment Area, Redevelopment Project Area And Redevelopment Project; Amending Ordinance No. 68971 and 67681; Authorizing The Execution Of A Redevelopment Agreement Between The City of St. Louis And St. Louis Food Hub TIF, Inc.; Prescribing The Form And Details Of Said Agreement; Designating St. Louis Food Hub TIF, Inc. As Developer Of A Portion Of Redevelopment Project Area 3; Making Certain Findings With Respect Thereto; Authorizing Other Related Actions In Connection With The Redevelopment Of Certain Property Within Redevelopment Project Area 3; And Containing A Severability Clause.
